下級法院既案例<br />\n仲不符現實？<br />\n區諾軒大聲公向上離咁遠，又可用sunny leung擺個大聲公係正黑警耳前既案例？"},{"pid":"ce99aa168654a9ee5d166ffed4136b370b001f92","tid":2058312,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:39:07.000Z","msg":"<del>法官形容辯方提出的私人檢控或司法覆核是瑣碎無聊及具壓迫性，直言覆核勝算不大，亦相信律政司定會介入相關私人檢控，並撤銷申請。</del><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢條黨委法官都on9<br />\n私人檢控或司法覆核係另一單case,已經唔係你審<br />\n有司法迫害時,胡國興班老鬼話唔評論其他法官審案<br />\n呢條友干涉其他案件又點計"},{"pid":"fba25392ffccd757ef237502bbdb2bbf4d81f272","tid":2058312,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:39:29.000Z","msg":"點解要post犬陽條link?"},{"pid":"bd83c03efd9b5fd1d69ce60fa5c55ec2e25548a4","tid":2058312,"uid":34755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:39:30.000Z","msg":"冇架 俾唔到實際阻嚇對面就會係咁架啦 <br />\n中國人特質 唔見棺材唔流眼淚"},{"pid":"ddda515646e9786a1c2f6e341ca587d1f0724f07","tid":2058312,"uid":337899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:41:12.000Z","msg":"有冇當年案例LINK?"},{"pid":"9ce883b91cb8cb8b1f3fbe8b77952f4339e4ed2a","tid":2058312,"uid":36845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:42:51.000Z","msg":"你講個案例係點"},{"pid":"2f280626c04dffe268d8f62b11d7d7f6ddabae8e","tid":2058312,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"478c52e5948ca32cbec3416c2b7a70c19c7e0d2e","tid":2058312,"uid":318980,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:31:40.000Z","msg":"呢個決定可以好嚴重<br />\n等同POPO將來做調查唔洗跟法例"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:42:58.000Z","msg":"辯方有冇用呢一點拗？"},{"pid":"080f64b9912ac7ddfcb3264d5fba967be0955a9b","tid":2058312,"uid":72457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:43:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n泥頭車成人都比人捉嫁啦"},{"pid":"86efd5e50d3e7aa7bbd92937e86cdf96e2af11db","tid":2058312,"ui